{"tid":1265330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"48歲洪欣仙女下凡  與張丹峰和好如初　","createTime":"2019-06-29T06:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T07:43:32.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33d28a707be331a3486a7e2cf85f204ce43f61a5","tid":1265330,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"藝人洪欣早前就丈夫張丹峰涉「出軌風波」，一度將夫妻倆的大部分合照、互動全部刪除，事件過去後，一家人又再和好如初，洪欣的心情也輕鬆了很多。 <br />\n<br />\n洪欣今日在微博分享扮靚心得，展示她在出席活動前的一套穿搭。在視頻中，洪欣先向大家展示了自己選擇的耳環，這是一個白色花瓣形狀的耳環，她說雖然這個耳環是白色的，看起來很簡單，但是因為是花瓣形狀，很有設計感，優雅、知性，卻也帶着一點少女心，給人一種溫婉小女人的氣質，而她身穿今年流行的綠色透明襯衫，搭配亮片閃閃的薄荷綠半身裙，清新亮眼，戴上花瓣耳環後，笑稱穿仙女裙搭配得剛剛好，看來心情大好的洪欣已重拾自信，重回顏值巔峰。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLxXYMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLxXYMw.png&h=b5681838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">西&hellip;西&hellip;西仙女！</span>"},{"pid":"c49612acb4effa3deb4283a9f202c4b4a03a6386","tid":1265330,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"29af88aa139f3375cfced7ddc6be35661df109e1","tid":1265330,"uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvbYJd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvbYJd4.gif&h=e12aa964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc3f152c21bb2ac61582843349b11233ca095db8","tid":1265330,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b96qoeS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb96qoeS.gif&h=f83ae837&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aa5c1b7f44d0abb11bd035f0131d16dd178e16d","tid":1265330,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQkCemJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna